==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Routine
<hw>Rou*tine"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>route</ets> a path, way, road. See <er>Route</er>,
<er>Rote</er>repetition.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A round of business,
amusement, or pleasure, daily or frequently pursued; especially, a
course of business or offical duties regularly or frequently
returning.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Any regular course of action or procedure rigidly
adhered to by the mere force of habit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Routinism</ent>⟦br⟧
